ELinks


	2002
	2003
	Jonas Fonseca <fonseca@diku.dk>






	This manual has been written to provide a complete user
	reference manual to ELinks. ELinks is an advanced text mode WWW
	browser, supporting colors, frame and table rendering,
	background downloading, full menu driven configuration
	interface and slim portable code.  Different file formats can
	be associated with external viewers natively or via mailcap.







